<p class="acahomeheader"><font color="#0000ff">IMPORTANT INFORMATION  <span class="acahomesubheader">(Please read before purchasing a sporting license):</span></font></p>
<p class="acaothertext">1)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;You will need a valid Drivers License in order to purchase a license through our online system.<br>2)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;We accept Visa and Mastercard for payment of your licenses, donations and other purchases.<br>3)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Fishing Licenses, Trapping Licenses and Marine Registrations&nbsp;<strong><em>MUST be printed immediately upon completion of the sale.</em></strong> This will serve as your legal license document. You will not receive anything in the mail. Please be sure to have a printer available upon purchase.<br>4)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Hunting Licenses and privileges and associated carcass tags must be mailed.&nbsp;<i style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;"><strong>Please allow 10-14 business days for receipt</strong>. </i>&nbsp;Please visit a License Issuing Agent if you wish to hunt immediately.<br>5)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;First time users of this website who previously held a NY sporting license must enter their name and date of birth exactly as it appears on your sporting license so that your existing record can be located and accessed.<br>6)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;If you have any questions or need assistance, please call&nbsp;1-866-933-2257, Monday - Friday between the hours of 8:30 AM and 4:30 PM.</p>
